ries  services  marketing and branding  leadership  see also  references historyedit hudson global inc was originally spun off as hudson highland group nasdaq  hhgp on march   from the former eresourcing and executive search business units of tmp worldwide inc  a human capital provider on april   hudson announced a corporate name change to hudson global inc and companys shares began trading in nasdaq under its new symbol hson from april   hudson was founded in  and was previously part of the tmp worldwide group in  tmp worldwide group engaged in an unprecedented period of strategic acquisition buying  specialist recruitment companies worldwide to become one of the largest staffing companies in the world the recruitment division of tmp worldwide group demerged from the wider business on  april  to form hudson global resources and on the  january  hudson global resources ltd rebranded as hudson to provide a single brand identity with which to approach the market however the legacy of the business can be traced back to  organization and operationsedit hudson operates in  countries with three geographic business segments hudson americas based in new york city hudson asia pacific based in sydney hudson europe based in london  servicesedit in recent years hudson has made efforts to establish a reputation as more than just a recruiter and cement itself as a company thats offers end to end talent solutions as such they now also focus on everything from specialised professional staffing and interim management to recruitment process outsourcing and talent management services in various blog articles and press releases the company has claimed this move is in response to the changing nature of the global workplace and workforce  something they have since dubbed the new world of work hudson operates in a wide range of industries including banking and financial services sales and marketing it pharmaceuticals and more hudson delivers enterprise as well as smaller scale assignments to businesses operating in many industries its services focus on providing specialized professional staffing interim management and recruitment process outsourcing related project management management consulting and talent management services operating industriesedit financial services banking accounting capital markets insurance products human resources sales and marketing manufacturing and industrial supply chain and procurement retail consumer goods and services infrastructure and transportation services health and life sciences defense media and high tech defense and aerospace itt media  pr  advertising resources chemicals energy natural resources utilities public sector public sector servicesedit assessment  selection blended workforce solutions contract and temporary recruitment digital solutions employer branding  sourcing innovation ingenium technology leadership development organizational design  management outplacement  career transition permanent recruitment predictive talent analytics recruitment process outsourcing iso  certified risk management  compliance retained search specialty talent pools talent management marketing and brandingedit hudson formerly used the tagline from great people to great performance however in  the tagline was updated to great people great performance which appears on the companys logo leadershipedit chairman of the board jon chait march  till february  manuel marquez march  till may  david g offensend may  till present chief executive officer jon chait march  till february  manuel marquez march  till may  stephen nolan may  till present see alsoedit companies portal hudson global inc was spun off from tmp worldwide inc referencesedit  a b hudsoncom global website  a b hudson global inc company overview reuters retrieved  may    a b hudson announces corporate name ticker symbol change bloomberg  april  retrieved  may    a b sec filing  hudson spun off from the eresourcing and executive search business units of tmp worldwide