 in  countries with three geographic business segments hudson americas based in new york city hudson asia pacific based in sydney hudson europe based in london  servicesedit in recent years hudson has made efforts to establish a reputation as more than just a recruiter and cement itself as a company thats offers end to end talent solutions as such they now also focus on everything from specialised professional staffing and interim management to recruitment process outsourcing and talent management services in various blog articles and press releases the company has claimed this move is in response to the changing nature of the global workplace and workforce  something they have since dubbed the new world of work hudson operates in a wide range of industries including banking and financial services sales and marketing it pharmaceuticals and more hudson delivers enterprise as well as smaller scale assignments to businesses operating in many industries its services focus on providing specialized professional staffing interim management and recruitment process outsourcing related project management management consulting and talent management services operating industriesedit financial services banking accounting capital markets insurance products human resources sales and marketing manufacturing and industrial supply chain and procurement retail consumer goods and services infrastructure and transportation services health and life sciences defense media and high tech defense and aerospace itt media  pr  advertising resources chemicals energy natural resources utilities public sector public sector servicesedit assessment  selection blended workforce solutions contract and temporary recruitment digital solutions employer branding  sourcing innovation ingenium technology leadership development organizational design  management outplacement  career transition permanent recruitment predictive talent analytics recruitment process outsourcing iso  certified risk management  compliance retained search specialty talent pools talent management marketing and brandingedit hudson formerly used the tagline from great people to great performance however in  the tagline was updated to great people great performance which appears on the companys logo leadershipedit chairman of the board jon chait march  till february  manuel marquez march  till may  david g offensend may  till present chief executive officer jon chait march  till february  manuel marquez march  till may  stephen nolan may  till present see alsoedit companies portal hudson global inc was spun off from tmp worldwide inc referencesedit  a b hudsoncom global website  a b hudson global inc company overview reuters retrieved  may    a b hudson announces corporate name ticker symbol change bloomberg  april  retrieved  may    a b sec filing  hudson spun off from the eresourcing and executive search business units of tmp worldwide inc reuters retrieved  may    a b c d e f hudson global management team  a b hudson q filed  july  irhudsoncom retrieved  nov    hudson global reports  first quarter results hudson investor relations website retrieved  may    employer branding  sourcing innovation hudson retrieved  november    hudson australia website hudson retrieved  nov    hudson us website hudson retrieved  nov    hudson uk website hudson retrieved  nov    hudson rpo hudson retrieved  october    case study  hudson global inc ogilvyprcom retrieved  october    trade marks application from hudson global inc  from great people to great performance pdf wwwipdgovhk retrieved  october    advertising slogans wikiquoteorg retrieved  october    hudson global office locations hudson retrieved  nov    a b jon f chait profile forbes retrieved oct     a b hudson global inc terminates chairman and chief executive officer jon chait reuters retrieved oct     a b manuel manolo marquez chairman and ceo of hudson global inc us visamsnbc news  may   msnbcmsncom retrieved oct     a b hudson global names stephen no